{
  "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.03,
      "size": 48528,
      "text": "一个矩阵可以看作对整个平面的变换，它会把每个向量拉伸、旋转或错切到新的位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "大多数向量在变换后，方向都会发生改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.13,
      "size": 50112,
      "text": "但有一些特殊的向量，变换之后方向纹丝不动，只是被拉长或压短，它们就是特征向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "transform",
      "line_id": "transform-1",
      "filename": "transform-transform-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/transform-transform-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "看这一圈蓝色的向量，当矩阵作用上去，它们纷纷偏转到了不同的方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "transform",
      "line_id": "transform-2",
      "filename": "transform-transform-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/transform-transform-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "而那几条彩色的向量始终躺在同一条直线上，方向完全没有改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "transform",
      "line_id": "transform-3",
      "filename": "transform-transform-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/transform-transform-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "这条方向不变的直线，就是这个矩阵的特征方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "eigen",
      "line_id": "eigen-1",
      "filename": "eigen-eigen-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/eigen-eigen-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.0,
      "size": 47952,
      "text": "特征向量在变换后被缩放的倍数，就是对应的特征值，通常记作希腊字母兰姆达。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "eigen",
      "line_id": "eigen-2",
      "filename": "eigen-eigen-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/eigen-eigen-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.37,
      "size": 53856,
      "text": "如果特征值大于一，向量被拉长；介于零和一之间，向量被压短；等于负数，方向还会翻转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "eigen",
      "line_id": "eigen-3",
      "filename": "eigen-eigen-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/eigen-eigen-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.76,
      "size": 44208,
      "text": "用一句公式概括就是，矩阵乘以特征向量，等于特征值乘以这个特征向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "solve",
      "line_id": "solve-1",
      "filename": "solve-solve-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/solve-solve-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49536,
      "text": "对二阶矩阵，特征值满足一个二次方程，一次项是矩阵的迹取负，常数项是行列式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "solve",
      "line_id": "solve-2",
      "filename": "solve-solve-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/solve-solve-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.73,
      "size": 43632,
      "text": "解出这个方程，判别式大于零就有两个不同的实特征值，等于零则是重根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "solve",
      "line_id": "solve-3",
      "filename": "solve-solve-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/solve-solve-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.5,
      "size": 56016,
      "text": "如果判别式小于零，特征值成了复数，平面内就找不到方向不变的实向量了，旋转矩阵正是如此。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "切换到对称矩阵，你会发现它的两条特征向量恰好相互垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "再看剪切矩阵，它只有一条特征方向，因为出现了重根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "特征向量是变换下方向不变的向量，特征值是它被缩放的倍数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.89,
      "size": 46224,
      "text": "它们揭示了矩阵最本质的骨架，广泛用于主成分分析、振动模态和量子力学。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "eigen-visualization",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/eigen-visualization/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "看清了特征结构，就看清了一个线性变换的灵魂，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 44.78000000000001,
  "total_size": 716256
}